description:
Friday Friend, Alex Berenson, joins C&B to take on CDC Director Rochelle Walensky's outrageous claims about masks. Why are covid cases surging in highly vaccinated Europe? The woke covid mob focuses on Green Bay quarterback, Aaron Rodgers. MSNBC guest on Winsome Sears: “There is a black mouth moving but a white idea running on the runway of the tongue of a figure who justifies and legitimates the white supremacist practices.” BLM and "Defund the Police" are now negative factors for democrats.
